<div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000091 0%, #1e1e78 100%); color: white; padding: 3rem 0; margin: -2rem -1rem 2rem -1rem; text-align: center;">
  <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1rem;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1rem;">üìã D√©claration d'Absence</h1>
